  "body": "It should not be better (logically speaking) to use the wrong `initialOwner` param in event instead of force using `address(0)`?\r\n\r\nIt always will be `address(0)` in that case but I would use the param instead.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/2ec2ed96950a6f67a83ea72596bb464b5f4ebd88/contracts/access/Ownable.sol#L39-L41\r\n\r\nAlso applies here https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/contracts/access/Ownable.sol#L86\r\n",
